# Install the Atom Editor

See [https://atom.io/docs/latest/getting-started-installing-atom](https://atom.io/docs/latest/getting-started-installing-atom)

* Goto [https://github.com/atom/atom/releases](https://github.com/atom/atom/releases)
* Download the .deb package
* Install with: sudo dpkg -i atom-amd64.deb

Inside Atom, install the following customization themes:

* UI-Theme: One Light
* Syntax Theme: One Light